  <text>
    <body><div type="letter">
      <p>St James' Sqre Weddy 5 o'clock</p>
      <p>Dearest W. I am setting out this evening for Esher, where I sleep tonight. I have not time to explain to you the why of all this change. But I shall probably ride over to Ockham</p>
      <p>tomorrow afternoon, tho' whether to sleep I do not yet know, as it depends on things I cannot foresee yet. I believe we are to set out on Friday on our tour.</p>
      <p>No more, dear, now. Thanks for letter.</p>
    </div></body>
